Description: Zwipe AS is a Norway-based biometric technology company. It focuses on the development and commercialization of secure, fast and easy-to-use biometric authentication solutions, primarily in the payment industry. Zwipeâ€™s technology solution enables simple and cost-efficient biometric authentication solutions in space- and power-constrained environments such as cards and wearables. The Company provides such services as Zwipe Pay, a platform providing a complete solution for any card manufacturer to deliver their own biometric payment cards and Zwipe Access, a biometric smart card solution for access control. Zwipe AS has operations in 12 countries and has a few subsidiaries: Zwipe Germany GmbH, Zwipe UK Ltd and Zwipe Singapore Pte.
